        <item>
            <title>Casio 推出全新手表戒指，外观俨如小型 G-Shock 可显示时间兼计时</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/casios-first-watch-ring/parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=casios-first-watch-ring</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/casios-first-watch-ring/parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 05:00:27 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CASIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[G-Shock]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智能戒指]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275522</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近来陆续有厂商推出智能戒指，而 Casio 最近推出的戒指虽然不是那么「智能」，但仍然相当实用。<br /><span id="more-1275522"></span></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63176"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_43hR7QccSM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_01jp-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_01jp-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_01jp.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这款型号为 CRW-001-1JR 的手表戒指是为了庆祝 Casio 推出数码手表 50 周年而制作，外观仿似 Casio 在 1983 年推出的经典全金属 G-Shock 5000 手表，在不足一吋的表壳下，仍然可以显示时、分、秒。戒指还配备三个功能按钮，可控制额外功能，如显示日期、不同时区时间和码表功能。此外竟然更具备背光功能，可以选择闪烁显示取代声音的闹钟功能。手表由单一电池供电，Casio 表示可使用约两年，而且易于更换。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_02jp-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_02jp-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_02jp.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Casio 表示，为了精确重现这款戒指手表所基于的大型数码手表的设计和精致细节，采用了金属粉末注射成型工艺，将其制作成单一零件。而 CRW-001-1JR 的尺寸只有日规 22 号（香港的 24 号）。如果是手指较小的用家，可以使用附带的垫片（日规 19/16 号，香港 22/18 号）来改善配戴效果。CRW-001-1JR 将于 12 月在日本上市，售价 19,800 日圆（约 128 美元）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw001_packagepngcop-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw001_packagepngcop-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw001_packagepngcop.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.casio.com/jp/watches/casio/product.CRW-001-1/">Casio</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/casios-first-watch-ring/parts/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
